<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Thank You for My Birthday Wishes!</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/js-confetti@latest/dist/js-confetti.min.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1 class="main-title">A Heartfelt Thank You!</h1>
        <p class="message" id="thankYouMessage">
            To all my amazing friends, family, and loved ones,<br><br>
            Thank you so much for all your wonderful birthday wishes, messages, calls, and thoughtful gifts! Your love and kindness truly made my day special and unforgettable. I feel incredibly lucky to have you all in my life.<br><br>
            With much love and gratitude,
            <br>
            [Your Name Here]
        </p>
        <p class="click-prompt">(Click anywhere on the message to celebrate!)</p>
    </div>

    <script src="script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>